column2: b'K: Seven Stories Movie 4 - Lost Small World - Ori no Mukou ni'

b'Misaki Yata is a youth whose reckless and immature attitude has led him to be shunned by his classmates. Saruhiko Fushimi is a loner who views the world in a pessimistic way. Despite being polar opposites, the two become the best of friends.\n\n(Source: TubiTV)'
